title: Hoops Tonight - NBA Power Rankings: Will Jayson Tatum & Jaylen Brown take Celtics back to Finals?
itunes:title: Hoops Tonight - NBA Power Rankings: Will Jayson Tatum & Jaylen Brown take Celtics back to Finals?
description:
Jason Timpf breaks down the Boston Celtics ahead of the 2022-2023 NBA season. How were the Celtics able to improve their roster this offseason? Will Ime Udoka's suspension have major consequences? And what steps must Jayson Tatum and Jaylen Brown make to take Boston back to the NBA Finals? #Volume #herd

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
